\emph default
: Clubs, Diamonds, Hearts, and Spades, and the 13 
\emph on
ranks
\emph default
: 2, 3, 4, \SpecialChar \ldots{}
, 10, Jack (J), Queen (Q), King (K), and Ace (A).
