\begin_inset Formula ${n \choose 3}$
\end_inset

 conditions three at a time, and so on, until they satisfy the 
\begin_inset Formula ${n \choose n}=1$
\end_inset

 condition including all 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 events.
