 The sample space would be
\begin_inset Formula \[
S=\left\{ HHH,\ HTH,\ THH,\ TTH,\ HHT,\ HTT,\ THT,\ TTT\right\} .\]

\end_inset

Now let 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

