\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Again it is clear that 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)\geq0$
\end_inset

 and we check that 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum f(x)=1$
\end_inset

 (see Equation 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:geom-series"

\end_inset

