\end_inset

We will find in the next section that the mean and variance are
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
\mu=\frac{1-p}{p}=\frac{q}{p}\mbox{ and }\sigma^{2}=\frac{q}{p^{2}}.\end{equation}

\end_inset


