\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 theirs, then 
\begin_inset Formula $Y=X+1$
\end_inset

.
 Consequently, they have 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{Y}=\mu_{X}+1$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{Y}^{2}=\sigma_{X}^{2}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

