\begin_inset Formula $f_{Y}$
\end_inset

 defined by
\begin_inset Formula \begin{equation}
f_{Y}(y)=\sum_{\{x\in S_{X}|\, h(x)=y\}}f_{X}(x)\end{equation}

\end_inset

 
\end_layout

