\end_layout

\end_inset

, which give the PDF, CDF, quantile function, and simulate random variates,
 respectively.

\color none
 
\color inherit
If 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=1$
\end_inset

 then 
\begin_inset Formula $X\sim\mathsf{exp}(\mathtt{rate}=\lambda)$
\end_inset

.
 The mean is 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu=\alpha/\lambda$
\end_inset

