\begin_inset Formula $\alpha^{\text{th}}$
\end_inset

 event occurs then 
\begin_inset Formula $Y\sim\mathsf{gamma}(\mathtt{shape}=\alpha,\,\mathtt{rate}=\lambda)$
\end_inset

.
