\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "rem:cov0-not-imply-indep"

\end_inset

Unfortunately, the converse of Corollary 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "cor:indep-implies-uncorr"

\end_inset

