 Let
\begin_inset Formula \[
X_{i}=\begin{cases}
1, & \mbox{if the \mbox{i}\mbox{th} fish is a bass,}\\
0, & \mbox{if the \mbox{i}\mbox{th} fish is a bluegill.}\end{cases}\]

\end_inset


