\emph on
underestimate
\emph default
 the true value of 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{2}$
\end_inset

.
 We use 
\begin_inset Formula $n-1$
\end_inset

 so that, on the average, our estimator of 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma^{2}$
\end_inset

 will be exactly right.
 
\end_layout

