\end_inset

The quantity 
\begin_inset Formula $z_{\alpha/2}^{2}/4E^{2}$
\end_inset

 is large enough to guarantee 
\begin_inset Formula $100(1-\alpha)\%$
\end_inset

 confidence.
\end_layout

