 not commit.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Type
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

II
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset

Error if we fail to reject 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{0}$
\end_inset

 when in fact 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{1}$
\end_inset

 is true.
