 for all vectors 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}\neq\mathbf{0}$
\end_inset

, then we say that 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{A}$
\end_inset

 is 
\emph on
positive semidefinite
\emph default
.
 If strict inequality holds for all 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{x}\neq\mathbf{0}$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{A}$
\end_inset

 is 
